{
  "stem": "10252.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was still there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to my-- my street, and I went to my-- my home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- three families, three communist families were living in this house right now.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we looked around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, from nowhere, I started to tell my husband that, you see, this is where the German soldiers came into the house and asked me to leave in the ghetto when they were taking us away.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I wanted a glass of water, and I went to get it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he said [SPEAKING GERMAN] And nobody ever told me to get out in my life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was a spoiled little girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the harshness, I'll never forget that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I started to explain this to my husband, that here I was in this room, and then the Germans soldiers were in this room.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, all I could see is German soldiers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So Stuart--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's the most amazing thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so Stuart got nervous, and he took me out of my home, thinking that once I'm out of the house, it will pass.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we got back in the car, and we started to drive around in town.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I saw the soldiers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw-- and the worst part of it is I saw all the Hungarian Sandor.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sandor was a policeman on a horse with a big rooster's [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] feather in his hat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I saw them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I saw them on every corner, and I saw them-- they-- [SOBBING] [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] I saw them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 17 SECONDS] I don't know what they did to me, these guys, but every time I think of them-- that's-- this part is tough.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were Hungarian Nazis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was easy for them just to get off their horse and beating on people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Being Jewish is a good cause.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they were everywhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were everywhere.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could see them everywhere.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Civil rights?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't think those were-- existed among the Jews in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My father was beaten before he was killed for stealing an apple in concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I don't eat apples.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we left the town and went back to Budapest, and everything was fine the next day.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was a very strange experience.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How did I--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother remarried, and my stepfather and I were brought here by my uncle.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uncle Micky, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He brought us out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He brought my aunts, my-- myself, my mother, and stepfather.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I came to America in 1951, November 30th.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And just about this Christmas, I already was working.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know Jay Thorpe?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jay Thorpe.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Department stores.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You wouldn't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You're too young.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was on 57th Street, and I didn't speak a word of English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I started to work as a junior model.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On the floor, I was modeling, because you didn't need to speak English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then 1955, I got married.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] 1956, I had my first child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His name is Kenneth, who is now a doctor. 1958, I had my daughter, Cherie, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who's married and has two children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, Well, I think that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in America, the belief that it can't happen is a very scary notion.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think being married to an American and having American children, I understand how they don't understand that it can happen again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's very important that we do what we do just now.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't enjoy doing what I'm doing, telling you my life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's very private, and it hurts me to tell you, because I don't want anyone to know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I'm doing it because I think this is important.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And if everyone will pitch in and do what I'm doing, and-- and-- and my children will do it and your children will do it, maybe-- maybe they won't hate us so much.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is my mother, Lily Bohm, before she was taken to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That is my father, Laszlo Schonfeld, about five years before the war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was one of the pictures that survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Mother and I on vacation in a seaside town, I think.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It-- I-- it looks like I'm two years old there, maybe less.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is a friend.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know who he is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] That is Uncle Bela Bohm, who survived the war but died later in a drowning accident.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
